reviewText: Brilliant!  You guys rock.  Also check out such books as "Agony of Victory: Assignment One."
I watched this dvd like 100 times in the last 24 hours and let me tell you that these guys are red hot!!  And that bass player...the hottest of all!

The concert is great, but there's tons of bonus features.  Unfortunately some artifacts though due to the DVD compression.  But if you're a fan, it's a must have.  My favorite is either "The Breakup Of LUZER" short film or Dan Seeth's "5 Steps To Stay Home Sick".  Classic stuff, and a great concert.
